    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in good condition and has been well-maintained throughout its ownership. The engine and transmission are smooth and reliable, making it an excellent choice for a dependable daily driver. While the exterior and interior are generally clean, you will find some minor signs of normal wear, such as a few light stone chips on the hood and slight creasing on the driver's seat bolster. Overall, it is a solid, honest car that is ready for its next owner without needing immediate repairs.",
