    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle in truly showroom condition. Meticulously preserved and showing no signs of wear, this unit has been held to the highest standards of maintenance and care. From the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior, every detail reflects its investment-grade status. For the discerning enthusiast who accepts only the best, this vehicle offers an unparalleled driving experience and lasting value.",
